ing: 1 (3.5 ounce) package instant vanilla pudding mix
des: "What could be simpler? Instant pudding mixed with cherry pie filling and yogurt! Excellent served with whipped topping."
ins: In a large bowl combine yogurt and instant vanilla pudding. Mix well. Stir in cherry pie filling.  Pour filling into pie crust and chill for 30 to 60 minutes.
